<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chunga Lautha hung leng inla,
 Mi tin lunggilah hung chengin
 Ka khutsuok uh In tawm nuoi ah,
 Kumkhuon Lautha'n hung chengin

[V2]
 Aw hung chengin
 Lung gilo dawngkawt hawng kit in la
 Lopina Lalpa
 Mitin lunggil ah hung chengin
 Lei mihing khutsuok tawm tak
 Na Temple in hung chansak in la
 Mi tin lunggil ah hung cheng in.

[V3]
 2. Kuom bang luoh ding sau-In tawm
 Na In thiengtho hung hi hen la
 Tuona gamdai lengvan lummei
 Lautha'n vabang hung buolin

[V4]
 3. Lalpa Na vangsakna lopi
 Lawpin tunin ka chang kit tau
 Ka thilbawl uh ka thilpiek teu
 Na lopina hung hi hen.</lyrics>
<title>Aw Hung Cheng In</title>
<author>Sawngkhawkai</author>
<hymn_number>266</hymn_number>
</song>